OL,3,CHow ironstone mined from the Cleveland
OL,4,CHills helped build the world
OL,6,FRachel Bullock visits Land of Iron to
OL,7,Ffind out how materials mined from the
OL,8,FCleveland Hills helped shaped the
OL,9,Fworld as we know it.
OL,11,FBeneath the surface of the Cleveland
OL,12,FHills lies a resource which has shaped
OL,13,Fthe area's heritage and made its mark
OL,14,Facross the world.
OL,16,FThroughout the 19th century, villages
OL,17,Fand settlements in the North East
OL,18,Fflourished thanks to a burgeoning
OL,19,Fironstone mining industry.
