OL,3,CHow ironstone mined from the Cleveland
OL,4,CHills helped build the world
OL,6,FLand of Iron is built on the site of
OL,7,Fthe former Loftus mine in
OL,8,FSkinningrove, which was the first of
OL,9,Fdozens which would be built in the
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FIt remains the only active ironstone
OL,13,Fmine in the country - and tells the
OL,14,Fstory of the industry back where it
OL,15,Fall began.
OL,17,FAt its peak Cleveland's Steel industry
OL,18,Fwould account for up to a third of
OL,19,FGreat Britain's total iron output -
OL,20,Fproviding materials for projects
OL,21,Facross the world.
