OL,3,CHow ironstone mined from the Cleveland
OL,4,CHills helped build the world
OL,6,FNick Wesson from Land of Iron museum
OL,7,Fin Skinningrove said: "These were the
OL,8,Fdays of Empire. Iron and steel from
OL,9,Fhere were going across the British
OL,10,FEmpire. There were railways in Africa
OL,11,Fand India. The Tyne Bridge was built
OL,12,Fwith iron and steel from here, the
OL,13,FSydney Harbour Bridge.
OL,15,F"It's not an exaggeration. There are
OL,16,Fbeams in New York with Skinningrove
OL,17,Fand Dorman Long stamped on them."
OL,19,FThe industry was born almost by
OL,20,Faccident, through a chance meeting on
OL,21,Fa North Yorkshire beach.
