OL,3,CHow ironstone mined from the Cleveland
OL,4,CHills helped build the world
OL,6,FIn the September of 1847, Anthony Lex
OL,7,FMaynard approached Samuel Okey as he
OL,8,Fwas scouring Saltburn beach for traces
OL,9,Fof ironstone.
OL,11,FAs the two chatted, Maynard said he
OL,12,Fhad seen similar rocks on his own
OL,13,Fproperty. They agreed to look at it
OL,14,Ftogether and cut the first ironstone
OL,15,Fin Cleveland there and then.
OL,17,FOver the years that followed, a total
OL,18,Fof 83 mines sprung up across the area,
OL,19,Fdrawing workers from all corners of
OL,20,FEngland to work the land - some
OL,21,Fwalking from as far away as Cornwall.
