OL,3,CHow ironstone mined from the Cleveland
OL,4,CHills helped build the world
OL,6,FThey drilled the iron ore by hand in
OL,7,Fcramped, crowded and dark conditions.
OL,9,FSteve Hall from Land of Iron said:
OL,10,F"It's really difficult to imagine
OL,11,Fquite how hard a life they had. The
OL,12,Fthings that they had to put up with,
OL,13,Fespecially in the early days when they
OL,14,Fhad no unions to support them.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
